{"tid":1189260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[6月9日]買散裝油自救","createTime":"2019-06-06T17:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T07:08:42.000Z","uid":126675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7bae2d9810a0e0971a3128f09f7595fb40d431","tid":1189260,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"【趣聞導航】汽車冇油隨時停唔到車 買散裝油自救<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/car/daily/article/20181206/20561971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcar%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F20561971&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=e1923abf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcar%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F20561971&h=7125fa82\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/car/daily/article/20181206/20561971</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目前，全港有三間油站提供散裝油，分別是蜆殼、加德士及中石化</span>，而埃索及中石油則未有提供上述服務。<span style=\"color: red;\">蜆殼油站最多可買四升；加德士及中石化則可買五升及二升</span>。留意只有蜆殼會提供油罐（$20），另外兩個集團則必須自攜密封金屬器皿。散裝油不設油卡減價優惠，油價以當日正價計算。前往救車前，記得去五金店買漏斗或火水泵以便注入電油。一般而言，幾公升已夠驅車往附近油站重新為汽車入油。<br />\n<br />\n利申：人在歐洲，揸開車 買散裝油好常見<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/wtPyYrPGRcDt841c6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FwtPyYrPGRcDt841c6&h=c4e32880&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64b9f69006237325058a8aac16c9c7e17ba61116","tid":1189260,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/410/media/images/69784000/jpg/_69784589_molotov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F410%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F69784000%2Fjpg%2F_69784589_molotov.jpg&h=b4773d06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d566df2ef279348537bac0699deb64221734feb","tid":1189260,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s7Iy4nDA1Nw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs7Iy4nDA1Nw&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=ded8508c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s7Iy4nDA1Nw</a>"},{"pid":"ab0ad9f74db6a5fac33ffaa2a190d8f62b902065","tid":1189260,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/legxycY_KnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlegxycY_KnI&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=b75b37b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/legxycY_KnI</a>"},{"pid":"914e306b8ac8c891fc9140fbc47cb10fa8db3629","tid":1189260,"uid":99324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878d85eb291fd3b43a60067a68a7e46ba7537e47","tid":1189260,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fa4f0c8803faa207e13b00f670f43699aaad66c","tid":1189260,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"係咪你擲油呀"},{"pid":"46eeeaf26a52e1f9b2300aa331a730d7518412dd","tid":1189260,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa4f0c8803faa207e13b00f670f43699aaad66c","tid":1189260,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"係咪你擲油呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"我係英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}